                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Buck</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Hay</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Tokyo</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1900-07-06">
                            <hi rend="italic">July 6, 1900</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Buck reports that altogether about 22,000 men have been ordered to China by
                    the Japanese Government.)</p>
